{/* Hero Section */}

CASTING
{/* Main Content Section */}

CASTING CALL

Riyadh Fashion Week is seeking talented models to showcase the latest designs from our featured designers. We welcome applications from models of all backgrounds who are passionate about fashion and ready to make their mark on the runway.

REQUIREMENTS

Female Models
  • Height: 5'8" (173cm) and above
  • Age: 16-25 years old
  • Professional portfolio
  • Previous runway experience preferred
Male Models
  • Height: 6'0" (183cm) and above
  • Age: 18-28 years old
  • Professional portfolio
  • Previous runway experience preferred
APPLICATIONS OPENING SOON
{/* Contact Section */}

GET IN TOUCH

For casting inquiries and more information about participating in Riyadh Fashion Week, please contact our casting team.

); }; export default Casting;
